Class Stick

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.peyrona.mingle.stick.Stick
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.peyrona.mingle.lang.interfaces.exen.IRuntime
    public final class Stick
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.peyrona.mingle.lang.interfaces.exen.IRuntime
    This class provides the execution environment where the transpiled Une code is executed.

    Although it is not frequent, several ExEn instances could coexists even in the same JVM: it is responsibility of the application that creates the instances to properly manage them.
